What I like to eat

Ever since I was a kid, I liked to try out new foods. As I got older, I tried to go to new restaurants and try out the different cuisines that the food had to offer. I've come a long way, but something still stay the same, as some of my favorite foods are:

  • pasta
  • hamburgers
  • pizza
and while I like each of them individually, if i had to rank how much i like each one of them. I would rank them like this
  1. pasta
  2. pizza
  3. hamburgers
